BuildDepends: gettext-dev, libiconv-dev, libncurses5 (>= 5.4-20041023-1006), libncursesw5 (>= 5.4-20041023-1001), fink (>= 0.24.12)
Depends: ncurses (>= 5.4-20041023-1006), libncurses5-shlibs (>= 5.4-20041023-1006), libncursesw5-shlibs (>= 5.4-20041023-1001), libiconv
GCC: 4.0
Source: ftp://ftp.mutt.org/mutt/%n-%vi.tar.gz
Source-MD5: 710bd56d3c4c4bcd1403bc4e053f7476
